Description: Digital photograph (colour); view of engraved rock art on rock surface, showing figure of unidentified quadruped with five or six apparent legs. Figure is upright and facing left, with long straight v-shaped horns. To the right a similar animal but unfinished. 10cm photo scale fitted at base of image. El-Kanais, Egypt. Scanned
